 I will always heal in the order of: chanter, tanks, then myself last, however you do need to make sure you don't die.  What good is a dead cleric?  DA is great.  1 second cast time, gives you 18 seconds to med, and gives the others time to taunt off ya or mez.  As soon as it pops off, you can blast a quick heal on yourself and be right back in action.<br>
